ccre.channel

Class BooleanFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.channel.BooleanFilter

  • public abstract class BooleanFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    A BooleanFilter is a wrapper that can be wrapped around any kind of Output, Input, InputPoll, or InputProducer, and will apply the same transformation in any case.

    skeggsc
